description: Decimal expansion of fifth root of 2.
comments: The sine of 2017 times this number is the near integer: 0.999999999999999978567771261.... - _Alonso del Arte_, May 03 2013
references: N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
links: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..20000
prog: (PARI) { default(realprecision, 20080); x=2^(1/5); for (n=1, 20000, d=floor(x); x=(x-d)*10; write("b005531.txt", n, " ", d)); } \\ _Harry J. Smith_, May 12 2009
crossrefs: Cf. A002950 = Continued fraction. - _Harry J. Smith_, May 12 2009
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_
